Backup and Recovery Guide
Backup Process

Steps to Create a Backup
1. Stop the application (optional but recommended)
2. Database Backup (if applicable)
3. Application Files Backup
4. Restart the application

Recovery Process
Steps to Restore from Backup
1. Stop the application (optional but recommended)
2. Restore the Database
3. Restore Application Files
 4. Restart the application

Backup Schedule
Daily Backups: Backups are scheduled daily at midnight using cron jobs.
Retention Policy: Backups older than 7 days are automatically deleted.

Storage Location
Local Backup Directory
Cloud Backup Location (if applicable)

Troubleshooting
Common Issues
1. Permission Denied
2. Incomplete Backups
3. Backup Corruption
   
